Cau hinh ngan chan MAC Flooding tren SW
int e0/3
switchport mode access
switchport port-security
switchport port-security maximum 4
switchport port-security violation shutdown
switchport port-security mac-address sticky



Tao service de code chay tu dong khi nhan log
sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/mac-flood-protect.service

[Unit]
Description=MAC Flooding Protector Script
After=network.target

[Service]
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 /opt/mac_flood_protect.py
Restart=always
User=root

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

sudo chmod +x /opt/mac_flood_protect.py
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable mac-flood-protect
sudo systemctl start mac-flood-protect
